    "body": "1. Please avoid abstract phrases like “ so slow” - it’s more likely that we can help if you show logs, say your erigon version, formulate problem more concreet. What speed you had in the past? \r\n2. I gave steps: https://github.com/ledgerwatch/erigon/issues/4006#issuecomment-1111797298   did you? \r\n3. @breezytm  try increase to 6?\r\n4. It will get faster with time: more peers, better geo locality of peers, we will create more our seed machines, we will get more experience with bittorrent protocol. \r\n5. snapshots are 2 times more compact than previous version of sync (need download 2 times less things): https://erigon.substack.com/p/disk-footprint-changes-in-new-erigon?s=r\r\n6. if you facing some unacceptable downtime: use —syncmode=full (it switch back to previous version of sync). ",
